Table: AISoc-Incidents
├── incident_id (String) ← Partition Key — format: "INC-{uuid4[:8]}"
├── timestamp (String) ← Sort Key — ISO 8601: "2024-01-15T10:30:00Z"
├── alert_type (String) ← e.g., "UnauthorizedAccess:EC2/SSHBruteForce"
├── severity (String) ← "LOW" | "MEDIUM" | "HIGH" | "CRITICAL"
├── resource_id (String) ← AWS resource ARN or ID
├── resource_type (String) ← "EC2" | "IAM" | "S3" | "RDS"
├── source_ip (String) ← IP address that triggered alert
├── agent_reasoning (String) ← Full reasoning text from Claude
├── action_taken (String) ← "QUARANTINE_TAG" | "REVOKED_KEY" | "IGNORED" | "ESCALATED"
├── action_result (String) ← "SUCCESS" | "FAILED" | "SKIPPED"
├── false_positive (Boolean) ← true/false
├── status (String) ← "OPEN" | "RESOLVED" | "INVESTIGATING"
└── raw_alert (String) ← Full JSON of original alert (stringified)
